{"tid":1634133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東網：工會指的哥撞人為交通事故　轟暴徒私了無法無天","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:07:21.000Z","uid":89966,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b25d7d8fd922626ead3b7bff217daaadc5a67a2","tid":1634133,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:40:15.000Z","msg":"長沙灣政府合署對出昨日(6日)有的士撞向人群，兩名女子被撞倒受傷，其中一人重傷。涉 事的士司機隨後被人拖落車圍毆，需送院治理。汽車交通運輸業總工會的士司機分會發表聲明，<span style=\"color: red;\">強烈譴責暴徒無法無天，濫用私刑圍毆的士司機，形容惡行令人髮指</span>。該會又指，自6月份以來，暴徒以不同方式堵塞交通主要幹道及隧道，造成全港多區交通擠塞，嚴重影響的士司機搵食生計，收入下跌逾30%至50%。<br />\n聲明指昨天下午在長沙灣政府合署附近出現非法集會及遊行，道路堵塞，嚴重影響交通及路面情況，並指<span style=\"color: red;\">「期間一輛的士發生交通事故」</span>，肇事的士車身被打砸破壞，司機更被抽出車外圍毆致頭破血流，工會就此向司機及其家屬致以慰問。<br />\n該會又指昨天發生事故後，<span style=\"color: red;\">理應隨即報警依法處理，不應濫用私刑圍毆的士司機至重傷</span>，呼籲的士司機在路面駕駛時要注意自身及乘客安全，如遇突發情況要冷靜處理，避免發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191007/bkn-20191007132101207-1007_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191007%2Fbkn-20191007132101207-1007_00822_001.html&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=6d0d2deb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191007/bkn-20191007132101207-1007_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n啱先去飛髮聽到班廢老係度話交通意外聽到R撚晒頭<br />\n返去google下原來係垃圾東網<br />\n咁都可以屈交通事故真係戇撚鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b7645ff9a789c8aa5b9e14613f9bbe19a3c199","tid":1634133,"uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"咁示威者打佢都係溝通事故 溝通意外啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7643001e30031fd066ee269c18b7dbcdb9e8b1a","tid":1634133,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2de78aefd0c28eb3ba55e4feea9a8e8b225c84","tid":1634133,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"那。呢d 就值得學習<br />\n咪撚再開埋d 分化 道歉post"},{"pid":"d4590a877c1d9bf2b5ccd893add0788ebffa8cc6","tid":1634133,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:58:08.000Z","msg":"交通意外都講得出口<br />\n有片睇架<br />\n咪當香港人發雞盲"},{"pid":"a0652e98fd4c3148b1f91702ac469f2b16e22e06","tid":1634133,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1613285/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1613285/page/1</a><br />\n又一驗證"},{"pid":"0c313154159027c98807565f4cf87cc8a81364ae","tid":1634133,"uid":72777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"東網都醒架嗱<br />\n內文所有野都係話工會講架咋 我只係純引述<br />\nSET晒防火牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9777126758eb7b4fa8e0755632a3449202c02712","tid":1634133,"uid":273760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"咁受害人就要追討賠償喇<br />\n實心奉勸各位<br />\n比人打到殘廢後又要賠錢好慘嫁<br />\n個受害人都係咁岩路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}